items.title: Vistara merger: Section of Air India pilots unhappy over different retirement age
items.description: In January 2022, Tata Group took control of Air India, along with its international budget subsidiary Air India Express

items.title: Zomato launches new 'Food Rescue' feature to reduce food wastage. All you need to know
items.description: Restaurant partners will continue to receive compensation for the original canceled order, plus a portion of the amount paid by the new customer if the order is claimed, Zomato said in a statement
